precis:
Amendment to the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD REGULATIONS which increases the
initial "sum certain" to be paid by the Board for the BASE GRADES of wheat
and amber durum wheat delivered in the 1994-95 crop year, effective
May 10, 1995.
